# uritemplate

Generate uritemplates according to RFC 6570 (not fully compatible yet). 

## Usage

- uritemplate: 
      
    (let [bitbucket (uritemplate "http://bitbucket.org/{user}/{project}")]
      (bitbucket :user "dfa" :project "uritemplate")) ; -> http://bitbucket.org/dfa/uritemplate

- uriparser: TBD
     	    
